     1	# Separate True Symmetries Canonicalization And Substantive Object Changes Before Claiming Support Stability
     2	
     3	When `support` is mission-central, freeze the smallest object that keeps exact
     4	bookkeeping honest before making any stability claim. In packet branches, that
     5	often means promoting packet identity above single-mode bookkeeping and treating
     6	conjugate completion as mandatory canonical representation rather than as the
     7	primary object itself.
